Package org.descripter.js

Utilities for descripting, interpretation, compilation, memory class loading, and so on.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bool
    A wrapper class for booleans.
    Descripter
    Represents a visitor to descript parsed JavaScript into Java source.
    Interpreter
    Represents a visitor to interpret parsed JavaScript.
    Memory
    Represents a memory class loader to compile Java source code on the fly.
    Visitor<S extends Script<?>>
    An abstract base class for JavaScript parser visitors.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    Abrupt
    An abstract base class for interpreting exceptions.
    Break
    An exception class used to interpret JavaScript break statements.
    Continue
    An exception class used to interpret JavaScript continue statements.
    Return
    An exception class used to interpret JavaScript return statements.
